    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently runs roughly and requires significant mechanical attention, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Cosmetically, the exterior has several large dents, significant paint peeling, and areas of surface rust, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is not currently in reliable driving condition and will likely need to be towed.",
      "price": 4500.0,
